text.tspan: Male vs. female suicide rate, 2000 to 2021
Estimated annual number of suicides per 100,000 males or females. Suicide deaths are underreported in many
countries due to social stigma and cultural or legal concerns. This data includes modeling based on global suicide
patterns, and includes adjustments and extrapolations that aim to account for missing data and underreporting.
Average annual change in female suicide rate
Average annual change in male suicide rate
Note: To allow for comparisons between countries and over time, this metric is age-standardized.
